design:
Change line 32 from:
font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
To:
font-family: 'Ubuntu', sans-serif;

For code block add: font-family: 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
For pre code block add: font-family: 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
Both selectors need this property added as the first property in their rule.

Add after help target:
changelog:
	@echo "# Changelog" > CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "## [Unreleased]" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "### Added" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@bd export --status=closed --type=feature 2>/dev/null | jq -r '"- " + .title + " (" + .id + ")"' >> CHANGELOG.md || echo "- None" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@echo "### Fixed" >> CHANGELOG.md
	@bd export --status=closed --type=bug 2>/dev/null | jq -r '"- " + .title + " (" + .id + ")"' >> CHANGELOG.md || echo "- None" >> CHANGELOG.md
